race.comment: TYCOON ZULU (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.08) in a Novice race at this track. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has ability and is a key runner. RUTHLESS ABBY (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.06) last time in a Novice race at this track. Should be in this for a long way. MAKO EIFFLER (5) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 488m behind Militaries (28.76) in a Novice race. Shapes as one to consider. NIGELLA GUNDI (1) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.
